Thai recipes: Chicken Ginger Stir-Fry Recipe: How to Make Chicken Ginger Stir-Fry 
15-3-2017 
A variation from the regular chicken recipes, Ginger Stir-Fry is a Thai dish and is an all time favourite delicacy to serve with rice. Made using chicken strips, mushrooms and spring onions, it is goes well with noodles too.



 
